// CONSISTENCY LEVELS:
// QUORUM: majority of replicas (strong, slower)
// LOCAL_QUORUM: majority within local data center (faster)
// ONE: single replica (fastest, weakest)
// ALL: all replicas (strongest, any failure = error)

